title: Siza Dlamini
text:
Siza Selby Dlamini (born 2 April 1976) is a <a href="Swaziland">Swazi</a> retired <a href="association%20football">football</a> striker. He has been capped for <a href="Eswatini%20national%20football%20team">Eswatini</a>. He was also named a top 10 <a href="COSAFA%20Cup">COSAFA Cup</a> Legend.
He served as an assistant coach for <a href="Jomo%20Cosmos">Jomo Cosmos</a> after his retirement.
